00:32:52.000 --> 00:32:58.000
 A string constant written as "I am a string" is an array of characters.

00:32:58.000 --> 00:33:05.000
 In the internal representation, the compiler terminates the array with the character backslash zero, so programs can find the end.

00:33:05.000 --> 00:33:11.000
 The length in storage is thus one more than the number of characters between the double quotes.

00:33:11.000 --> 00:33:22.000
