01:19:46.000 --> 01:20:02.000
 A sort often consists of three parts a comparison which determines the ordering of any pair of objects an exchange which reverses their order and a sorting algorithm which makes comparisons and exchanges until the objects are in order.

01:20:02.000 --> 01:20:07.000
